<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Us 🌟</title>
  <style>
    /* Background with gradient */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #74ebd5, #ACB6E5);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: #333;
    }

    /* Glassmorphism card */
    .container {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 40px;
      max-width: 850px;
      width: 90%;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.8em;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.1em;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #f0f0f0;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }

    ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 25px auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 15px;
    }

    ul li {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
    }

    ul li:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
    }

    a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 12px 28px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007BFF, #00C6FF);
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.4);
    }

    a:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0056b3, #008cff);
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* Animation */
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>About Us 🤝</h1>

    <p>Hello and welcome! 👋</p>

    <p>We’re a small team of developers passionate about building clean and helpful web applications. Our goal is to share knowledge, build useful tools, and have fun while doing it! 💡✨</p>

    <p>Here’s what we love working with:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>⚙️ Node.js - Powerful backend JavaScript runtime</li>
      <li>🚀 Express.js - Minimal and flexible web framework</li>
      <li>📝 EJS - Simple templating with JavaScript</li>
      <li>🎨 HTML & CSS - Web structure and styling</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Thanks for visiting our about page. We hope you enjoy exploring more! 🙏</p>

    <a href="/blog">📝 Visit Our Blog</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
